               stealing a fringed dimity petticoat, value 12 s. a pair of linen sheets, value 8 s. five linen shirts, value 40 s. five muslin stocks, value 6 s. four linen shifts, value 4 s. a pair of silk stockings, value 1 s. two pair of cotton stockings, value 3 s. four pair of worsted stockings, value 4 s. three linen mangle-cloths, value 3 s. a woman's<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177701150005"></xptr> linen cap, value 3 d. a man's cotton night-cap, value 3 d. a cotton night-gown, value 1 s. a flannel night-gown, value 1 s. a pair of muslin mittens, value 3 d. a muslin apron, value 6 d. three linen handkerchiefs, value 18 d. seven child's linen frocks, value 12 s. five dimity petticoats, value 2 s. a diaper petticoat, value 6 d. a flannel petticoat, value 2 d. two child's linen gowns, value 6 d. a pair of child's stays, value 1 s. five child's linen shirts, value 10 d. and seven pair of child's thread stockings, value 3 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17770115-2-victim77" type="victimName">
